Darkwind announcements are the game's official bulletin-board style
messages for important news, updates, and notices.

The current announcement system keeps track of read and unread messages
for each player separately.

Useful commands:

  checkannounce
      Shows how many announcement posts you have not read yet.

  announcehist
      Shows recent announcement history.

If you use the web client, announcements also appear in the dedicated
Announcements interface with read and unread status.

Announcements are staff-managed. Reading one marks it as read for you,
but it does not change whether the announcement itself is globally active
or archived.

See also: help checkannounce
